comment._content: I noticed a typing error in the title and the tag. Both give Hanroit, while it should be Hanriot. When doing a search within the SDASM Archives on the wrong term of Hanroit I got a lot of pictures, maybe 25 - 30. Although I am not that precise, I noticed this typing error when doing some research into the Hanriot machines.
